You do not get any thoughts from ego or superego.

584
00:31:24,644 --> 00:31:30,452
But there is wobbling in the Agnya because of your imbalanced ways.

585
00:31:30,584 --> 00:31:32,075
And the imbalanced ways are,

586
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:35,069
that sometimes you are with ego or with superego.

587
00:31:36,543 --> 00:31:39,239
This has happened to our people in the West

588
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:43,280
because we have had so much of ego we got really tired of it.

589
00:31:44,174 --> 00:31:45,383
We got frightened with it.

590
00:31:45,759 --> 00:31:50,596
Then we started taking to drugs and things to increase our superego.

591
00:31:51,353 --> 00:31:53,067
But by doing that what we are doing is

592
00:31:53,132 --> 00:31:55,555
pushing by one end and bringing back another end

593
00:31:55,624 --> 00:31:57,285
and that’s how we are wobbling

594
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:59,527
our ego and superego

595
00:31:59,724 --> 00:32:02,391
by which we are not helping ourselves at all.

596
00:32:02,986 --> 00:32:04,986
So what one has to do

597
00:32:05,106 --> 00:32:08,177
is to rise within oneself up to the point of Agnya

598
00:32:08,274 --> 00:32:10,292
and try to steady your Agnya.

599
00:32:10,841 --> 00:32:13,383
There are many people have asked Me one question.

600
00:32:13,401 --> 00:32:15,099
How to steady the Agnya?

601
00:32:17,129 --> 00:32:22,651
Agnya is placed at the crossing point of our nerves

602
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:24,316
and also optic thalamus.

603
00:32:24,714 --> 00:32:27,485
Now, so it is said that

604
00:32:27,566 --> 00:32:30,492
if you have wobbling eyes you’ll have a wobbling Agnya.

605
00:32:31,276 --> 00:32:32,806
You have to steady your eyes.

606
00:32:33,629 --> 00:32:34,701
You have to soothe them.

607
00:32:34,921 --> 00:32:40,773
Now it is very, very out of date, ancient, old

608
00:32:40,865 --> 00:32:44,264
and all sorts of names that you call it to a thing like that.

609
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:46,537
But you must steady your eyes and

610
00:32:46,629 --> 00:32:50,684
steady them in such a way that it is very soothing for the eyes.

611
00:32:51,212 --> 00:32:54,876
Which is the most soothing thing for the eyes is the green grass.

612
00:32:56,956 --> 00:33:01,378
If you could see the green grass with your eyes means you walk

613
00:33:02,366 --> 00:33:04,354
with your eyes on the ground.

614
00:33:05,416 --> 00:33:08,189
Your eyes will be soothed, your Agnya will be all right.

615
00:33:08,364 --> 00:33:10,203
That’s why Christ said that,

616
00:33:10,231 --> 00:33:13,504
“I tell you about the adulterous eyes”.

617
00:33:13,732 --> 00:33:15,801
He talked about adulterous eyes.

618
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:18,803
The eyes with which you do adultery.

619
00:33:20,530 --> 00:33:22,032
Is a very common thing these days.

620
00:33:22,132 --> 00:33:23,933
Every woman a man must see.

621
00:33:23,991 --> 00:33:25,405
Every man a woman must see.

622
00:33:26,342 --> 00:33:28,409
As if it is the most important job.

623
00:33:28,446 --> 00:33:30,641
If you have not seen one woman you’re finished.

624
00:33:31,707 --> 00:33:33,108
I mean this is being modern.

625
00:33:33,437 --> 00:33:35,356
But I am an old fashioned lady.

626
00:33:35,706 --> 00:33:38,760
And at the time of Christ he said,

627
00:33:38,930 --> 00:33:40,868
“You should not have adulterous eyes.”

628
00:33:41,181 --> 00:33:43,787
And the ones who have adulterous eyes are,

629
00:33:44,568 --> 00:33:49,751
no more than any other, but our Western Christians.

630
00:33:51,135 --> 00:33:54,249
Who all the time even in the church, even

631
00:33:54,309 --> 00:33:57,444
when they’re giving sermons, their eyes are moving with adultery.

632
00:33:58,437 --> 00:34:03,644
These eyes have to be very, very pure, very, very deep

633
00:34:03,756 --> 00:34:08,559
and very loving when you want to have your Agnya all right.

634
00:34:08,672 --> 00:34:10,403
Because you receive through you eyes.

635
00:34:11,316 --> 00:34:12,916
Say if you have closed your eyes

636
00:34:13,055 --> 00:34:15,072
you do not put your attention to anything because

637
00:34:15,086 --> 00:34:16,032
your eyes are closed.

638
00:34:16,175 --> 00:34:18,583
You are not adding more thoughts to yourself.

639
00:34:18,872 --> 00:34:22,045
But if your eyes are open you are adding much more thoughts

640
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:24,630
because everywhere the eyes go the attention goes

641
00:34:24,664 --> 00:34:27,521
and you see things and create thoughts and put in them.

642
00:34:27,597 --> 00:34:32,267
So your attention which has to go to the Spirit,

643
00:34:32,453 --> 00:34:34,103
which has to go to God,

644
00:34:34,401 --> 00:34:38,302
which has to shine through the window of Divine.

645
00:34:38,569 --> 00:34:41,958
This beautiful thing is ruined by

646
00:34:42,307 --> 00:34:46,082
the way we use our eyes and we do not respect it.

647
00:34:47,682 --> 00:34:54,682
There’s nothing so pure and beautiful as the grass on the ground

648
00:34:54,908 --> 00:34:57,987
or the ground itself, which takes our feet,

649
00:34:58,075 --> 00:35:02,178
which supports us, which looks after us, enriches us.

650
00:35:03,562 --> 00:35:05,937
We should put our eyes on the Mother Earth

651
00:35:06,035 --> 00:35:07,915
instead of looking at every person.

652
00:35:08,484 --> 00:35:11,437
But from Sahaja Yoga point of view now many of you know

653
00:35:11,441 --> 00:35:13,911
what happens to your eyes  when you look at somebody.

654
00:35:14,237 --> 00:35:18,270
Maybe a entity might enter your eyes.

655
00:35:18,689 --> 00:35:20,488
