00:39:21,775 --> 00:39:25,821
One has to think about all these things

729
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:28,712
in the proper light of Sahaja Yoga.

730
00:39:29,063 --> 00:39:30,605
Unless and until you are realized

731
00:39:30,739 --> 00:39:33,047
My talk is just useless for you.

732
00:39:33,781 --> 00:39:36,137
But once you are realized you will know

733
00:39:36,359 --> 00:39:38,555
that if you glance at someone

734
00:39:38,798 --> 00:39:41,422
you might suddenly get a headache at the back.

735
00:39:41,527 --> 00:39:44,534
You might feel a dart has gone into your head

736
00:39:44,552 --> 00:39:45,892
or something has happened.

737
00:39:45,992 --> 00:39:47,724
You might feel that you’re blinding

738
00:39:48,053 --> 00:39:53,024
with somebody’s face and you will get all kinds of experiences

739
00:39:53,054 --> 00:39:56,711
by which you will know how important are your eyes.

740
00:39:58,270 --> 00:40:01,405
All your nervousness and everything can be cured

741
00:40:01,699 --> 00:40:03,254
if you have pure eyes.

742
00:40:03,504 --> 00:40:05,039
But it is such a vicious circle

743
00:40:05,381 --> 00:40:07,645
that through your eyes you gather all the bad

744
00:40:07,734 --> 00:40:10,807
and is accumulated in the Agnya and you have to clear the Agnya

745
00:40:10,845 --> 00:40:12,296
to make the eyes clear.

746
00:40:13,143 --> 00:40:14,246
It’s a vicious circle.

747
00:40:14,733 --> 00:40:16,733
But it can start at a point as I said,

748
00:40:16,828 --> 00:40:18,302
we have to ask for forgiveness.

749
00:40:20,107 --> 00:40:27,079
Secondly we have to bring Christ in our Agnya Chakra.

750
00:40:29,482 --> 00:40:31,314
Thirdly we have to give up all

751
00:40:31,643 --> 00:40:35,724
drugs and all intoxicants and all smoking.

752
00:40:36,306 --> 00:40:39,576
That happens automatically when you are a Sahaja Yogi,

753
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,454
it will work out.

754
00:40:40,753 --> 00:40:45,800
But eyes express the whole of your being, your brain,

755
00:40:46,072 --> 00:40:50,483
your body, your limbs everything.

756
00:40:50,616 --> 00:40:56,120
And if your Agnya is all right then you eyes

757
00:40:56,578 --> 00:40:58,220
are perfectly all right.

758
00:40:58,414 --> 00:41:00,797
They emit nothing but love

759
00:41:01,395 --> 00:41:02,830
wherever they glance.

760
00:41:03,130 --> 00:41:06,977
Only with a glance of your eyes you can raise the Kundalini.

761
00:41:08,091 --> 00:41:12,371
Only with the glance of your eyes you can cure people.

762
00:41:12,845 --> 00:41:16,659
Only with your glance you can bring joy into

763
00:41:16,702 --> 00:41:19,090
the destroyed and the ruined people.

764
00:41:19,524 --> 00:41:23,064
So these eyes which you see are the windows

765
00:41:23,081 --> 00:41:25,377
